# Commercial Model

BCSentinel follows a deliberately limited institutional licensing strategy.

Annual licenses provide continuous access to:

• The BCSentinel Platform

• Institutional Intelligence Packages

• Continuous Formation Monitoring

• Intelligence Updates

• Platform Improvements

• Dedicated Institutional Support

The objective is not to maximise the number of customers.

The objective is to maximise the value delivered to each institutional client.

---

# Why Institutions Pay

Institutions do not purchase blockchain data.

They do not purchase dashboards.

They do not purchase notifications.

They purchase earlier institutional understanding.

The value of BCSentinel is not measured by the quantity of information analysed.

It is measured by the quality, relevance and timing of the institutional intelligence delivered.

---

# Product Philosophy

BCSentinel has been designed around one principle.

The earlier an institution understands how a digital economic system is being formed, the greater its ability to conduct independent research, evaluate strategic relevance and make informed decisions before public visibility.

Future Formation Intelligence is the discipline that makes this possible.

